Package edu.ntnu.idatt2001.paths.models.player

Class Player

java.lang.Object
edu.ntnu.idatt2001.paths.models.player.Player
public class Player extends Object
A class that represents a player in a game. A player has different attributes that can be affected by a story A player has a name, health, score, gold and an inventory and represent who is playing the game. When a player has 0 or less health, the player is dead and the game is over.
Version:
0.2 - 11.04.2023
Author:
Helle R. and Sander S.
